<h2>Mediablox Framework (MBFW)</h2>

<p>The Mediablox Framework is a bespoke web development framework. It was developed as an in-house alternative to Bootstrap, Foundation, UI Kit etc. which have very oppinionated styles.</p>
<p>It started life as a form of InuitCSS by Harry Styles, which has now been adapted in as a dependency for continued updates.</p>
<p>The framework comprises of three core components, mbfw.scss, mbfw.js and mbfw.components.</p>

<ul>
	<li>
		<a href="https://github.com/mediablox/mb.mbfw.scss">mbfw.scss</a>
	</li>
	<li>
		<a href="https://github.com/mediablox/mb.mbfw.js">mbfw.js</a>
	</li>
	<li>
		<a href="https://github.com/mediablox/mb.mbfw.components">mbfw.components</a>
	</li>
</ul>

